      <body>
         <div>
            <pb facs="1864_08_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Gildemeister_Ries_Bremen_1.tif" n="envelope"/>
            <p>
               <seg rend="center">
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <placeName ref="K00515">v<hi rend="underline">ia
                                Mar</hi>seilles</placeName>
                  </hi>
                  <stamp type="postal" style="round">
                     <placeName ref="K00524">BREMEN</placeName>.TH.&amp;TX<lb/>
                     <date when="1864-08-09">9<lb/>8</date>
                     <lb/>5-6N</stamp>
                  <lb/> Mess<hi rend="superscript">s</hi>
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler + Co</orgName>
                  <lb/>
                  <stamp style="rectangular" type="postal">P.P.</stamp>
                  <stamp type="postal" style="round">TOUR-T<lb/>
                     <date when="1864-08-11">11<lb/>AOUT<lb/>64</date>
                     <lb/>
                     <unclear reason="faded">FORBAS II</unclear>
                  </stamp>
               </seg>
               <lb/>
               <seg rend="center">
                  <hi rend="latintype">paid <placeName ref="K00514">Nagasaki</placeName>
                     <lb/>
                     <placeName ref="K00502">Japan</placeName>
                  </hi>
                  <lb/>
                  <stamp type="postal" style="round">
                     <placeName ref="K00503">SHANG-HA<unclear reason="faded">E</unclear>
                     </placeName>
                     <lb/>
                     <date when="1864-09-24">23<lb/>SEPT.<lb/>64</date>
                     <lb/>BAU FRANCAIS</stamp>
               </seg>
               <add style="writingMode: vertical-lr; textOrientation: sideways-right" resp="other" place="marginRight">1864<lb/>
                  <placeName ref="K00524">Bremen</placeName>
                  <date when="1864-08-09">9 Aug</date>
                  <lb/>
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01095">Gildemeister Ries</orgName>
                  <lb/>R <hi rend="underline">
                     <date when="1864-10-01">1 Octh</date>
                     <lb/>
                     <date when="1864-10-04">4 Octh</date>
                  </hi>
               </add>
            </p>
            <pb facs="1864_08_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Gildemeister_Ries_Bremen_2.tif" n="2"/>
            <p>
               <hi rend="latintype">via <placeName ref="K00515">Marseille</placeName>
               </hi>
               <lb/>
               <seg rend="right">
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <placeName ref="K00524">Bremen</placeName>
                     <date when="1864-08-09">August 9 1864</date>
                     <lb/>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="center">Herren <hi rend="latintype">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler</orgName>
                  </hi>
                  <lb/>
               </seg>
               <lb/>
               <seg rend="right">
                  <placeName ref="K00514">Nagasaki</placeName>
               </seg>
               <lb/> Unter höflicher Bestätigung<lb/> unserer ergebenen Mittheilungen vom<lb/>
               <date when="1861-07-09">9 po</date>, von
                    denen Sie anderseitig <term type="logistic" ref="K01538">Du<lb/> plicat</term>
                    finden bekennen wir uns<lb/> zum Empfang Ihrer geschätzten<lb/> Zuschriften vom
                        <date when="1864-05-16">16 <hi rend="latintype">Mai</hi>
               </date> + <date when="1864-06-05">5 Juni</date>,<lb/> denen Inhalt wir uns
                    bestens an-<lb/> merken.<lb/> Wir entnahmen denselben<lb/>
               <term type="logistic" ref="K01515">Conaissement</term> + <hi rend="latintype">
                  <term type="commercial" ref="K01574">factura</term>
               </hi> über <hi rend="latintype">p<lb/>
                  <name type="ship" ref="K01726">Trave</name>
               </hi> von Ihnen verschiffte<lb/>
               <measure type="volume" quantity="261" unit="ballen" commodity="tobacco">261</measure>
               <hi rend="latintype">Ballen <term type="goods" ref="K01549">Taback</term>
               </hi> u. da diese Parthie innerhalb<lb/> unsres Ihnen für diesen Artikel<lb/>
                    gegebenen Limits einsteht, so<lb/> haben wir Ihnen, als unsern<lb/> halben
                    Antheil in der <hi rend="latintype">
                  <term type="commercial" ref="K01574">factura</term>
               </hi>,<lb/>
               <add resp="other" place="inline" style="transformRotateZ(-45deg)">
                  <hi rend="underline">not<lb/>m 375</hi>
               </add> $ 1593. 93 <seg rend="right">(nicht $ 159<hi rend="underline">8.</hi> 93
                        wie<lb/> sie aufgeben</seg>
               <lb/> gutgeschrieben u. betrachten die-<lb/> sen <hi rend="latintype">
                  <term type="goods" ref="K01549">Taback</term>
               </hi> als für gemeinschaft-<lb/> liche Rechnung mit Ihnen gehend,<lb/> nicht
                    zweifelnd, daß wir hierin<lb/> mit Ihnen Conform sind.<lb/> Assuranz auf den <hi rend="latintype">
                  <term type="goods" ref="K01549">Taback</term>
               </hi>
               <lb/> ist vorläufig gedeckt, u.<lb/> hoffen wir, daß diese Parthie<lb/> ein
                    befriedigendes Resultat<lb/> geben wird.<lb/>
            </p>
            <pb facs="1864_08_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Gildemeister_Ries_Bremen_3.tif" n="3"/>
            <p> Wir deckten dem Auftrag<lb/> Ihres Herrn <hi rend="latintype">
                  <persName ref="K00011">M. H. Gildemeister</persName>
               </hi> z<unclear reason="illegible">u-</unclear>
               <lb/> folge, einen Theil userer frü<unclear reason="illegible">he</unclear>
               <lb/> ren <hi rend="latintype">
                  <term type="commercial" ref="K01534">Tratten</term>
               </hi> für Ihre Rechnung<lb/> bei Herrn <hi rend="latintype">
                  <persName ref="K00038">F. Laeisz</persName>
               </hi> in <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00522">Hamburg</placeName>
               </hi>
               <lb/> durch unsere <term type="commercial" ref="K01523">Rimesse</term> an
                    denselben<lb/> von<lb/>
               <table>
                  <row>
                     <cell>Rf</cell>
                     <cell>
                        <measure type="currency" quantity="12000" unit="unclear">12000.-</measure>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>p <date when="1864-08-11">12</date>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>August</cell>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <cell>
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>"</abbr>
                           <expan>Rf</expan>
                        </choice>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>
                        <measure type="currency" quantity="1200" unit="unclear">1200.-</measure>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>p <date when="1864-08-08">8</date>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>do</abbr>
                           <expan>detto</expan>
                        </choice>
                     </cell>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <cell>
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>"</abbr>
                           <expan>Rf</expan>
                        </choice>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>
                        <measure type="currency" quantity="1000" unit="unclear">1000.-</measure>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>p <date when="1864-08-11">11</date>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>do</abbr>
                           <expan>detto</expan>
                        </choice>
                     </cell>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <cell>Rf</cell>
                     <cell>
                        <hi rend="underline">
                           <measure type="currency" quantity="14200" unit="unclear">14200</measure>
                        </hi>
                     </cell>
                     <cell>zusammen</cell>
                     <cell/>
                  </row>
               </table>
               <seg rend="right">
                  <add resp="other" place="inline" style="transformRotateZ(-45deg)">
                     <hi rend="underline">
                        <hi rend="latintype"/>
                     </hi>
                     <term type="commercial" ref="K01536">Mem 375</term>
                  </add>
               </seg>
               <lb/> wofür wir Sie à 138 1/8 mit Gr
                        <measure type="currency" quantity="653766" unit="unclear">653766</measure>gt<lb/> belasteten, um conforma <hi rend="underline">p<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> 6 dieser</hi>
               <lb/> Buchung bittend.<lb/> Es ist mit Geld dies seits<lb/> fortdauernd sehr
                    knapp u. sind<lb/> Waarenpreise in Folge davon,<lb/> sowie in Folge der
                    unsicheren poli<lb/> tischen Verhältnisse durchgehend<lb/> gedrückt. Besonders
                    wirken die<lb/> amerikanischen Zustände entmu-<lb/> thigend; es sind von <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00531">NewYork</placeName>
               </hi>
               <lb/> starke Rückverschiffungen ver-<lb/> schiedener Produkte, unter<lb/>
                    anderem auch <gap quantity="3" unit="char"/> von <hi rend="latintype">
                  <term type="goods" ref="K01571">Thee</term>
               </hi>,<lb/> nach <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00511">Europa</placeName>
               </hi> gemacht, u. müssen<lb/> solche Manipulationen die des-<lb/> seitigen
                    Märkte natürlich<lb/> stark drücken.<lb/> Wir freuen uns, die </p>
            <pb facs="1864_08_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Gildemeister_Ries_Bremen_4.tif" n="4"/>
            <p>verschiedenen Parthien<lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <term type="goods" ref="K01571">Thees</term>
               </hi> + die <hi rend="latintype">
                  <term type="goods" ref="K01524">Seide</term>
               </hi> realisirt zu<lb/> haben. Bis zur Ankunft der<lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <name type="ship" ref="K01726">Trave</name>
               </hi> haben wir dann hof-<lb/> fentlich günstigere Verhältnisse<lb/>
               <seg rend="center">wir begrüßen Sie<lb/> mit freundschaftlicher</seg>
               <lb/>
               <seg rend="right">Ergebenheit<lb/>
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01095">Gildemeister+Ries</orgName>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
               <lb/>
               <add resp="unclear" place="inline" style="transformRotateZ(-45deg)">
                  <hi rend="latintype">frco</hi>
               </add>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1864_08_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Gildemeister_Ries_Bremen_1.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>via Marseilles <lb/>BREMEN.TH.&amp;TX<lb/>9<lb/>8<lb/>5-6N<lb/>Messrs. L. Kniffler +
                Co<lb/>P.P. TOUR-T<lb/>11<lb/>AOUT<lb/>64<lb/>FORBAS II[?]<lb/>paid
                Nagasaki<lb/>Japan<lb/>SHANG-HAE[?]<lb/>23<lb/>SEPT.<lb/>64<lb/>BAU
                FRANCAIS<lb/>⟨1864<lb/>Bremen 9th Aug.<lb/>Gildemeister Ries<lb/>R[eceived] 1st
                Oct.<lb/>4th Oct.⟩</p>
         <pb facs="1864_08_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Gildemeister_Ries_Bremen_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>via Marseille<lb/>Bremen August 9th 1864<lb/>Messrs. L. Kniffler<lb/>
            <lb/>Nagasaki<lb/>Politely confirming our<lb/>respectful notices from <lb/>9th of
                last month, of which you will find a duplicate<lb/>on the back, we acknowledge<lb/>
                receiving your esteemed<lb/>letters from 16th May + 5th June,<lb/>the contents of
                which we have noted<lb/>attentively.<lb/>We gathered from the letters <lb/>the bill
                of lading + invoice for the<lb/>261 bundles of tobacco shipped by you <lb/>on the
                Trave and as this lot falls <lb/>within the limit we gave you for <lb/>this article,
                we have credited you, <lb/>as our half share of the invoice,<lb/>⟨notm 375⟩ $ 1,593.
                93 (not, as you <lb/>recorded, $ 1,598. 93)<lb/>and consider this tobacco<lb/>as
                going by shared account with you<lb/>and do not doubt that we are in<lb/>this matter
                in accordance with you. <lb/>Insurance for the tobacco <lb/>is covered for the
                moment and<lb/>we hope that this shipment <lb/>will bring about a satisfying
                <lb/>result.</p>
         <pb facs="1864_08_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Gildemeister_Ries_Bremen_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <p>We covered, in accordance with the <lb/>of your Mr. M. H. Gildemeister,<lb/>a part of
                our earlier bills of <lb/>exchange for your account with <lb/>Mr. F. Laeisz in
                Hamburg<lb/>by means of our remittance to him <lb/>of<lb/>
            <table>
               <row>
                  <cell>Rf</cell>
                  <cell>12,000.-</cell>
                  <cell>p 12</cell>
                  <cell>August</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>"</cell>
                  <cell>1,200.-</cell>
                  <cell>p 8</cell>
                  <cell>id.</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>"</cell>
                  <cell>1,000.-</cell>
                  <cell>p 11</cell>
                  <cell>id.</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>Rf</cell>
                  <cell>
                     <hi rend="underline">14,200</hi>
                  </cell>
                  <cell>together</cell>
                  <cell/>
               </row>
            </table> ⟨Mem 375⟩<lb/>for which we debit you at 138 1/8 with<lb/>Gr 653766gt and
                ask that you book this in <lb/>conformity per 6th of this month.<lb/>There is a
                continuous shortage <lb/>in terms of money over here and <lb/>consequently the
                prices of goods,<lb/>also due to the uncertain political <lb/>conditions here, are
                constantly <lb/>depressed. Especially the American <lb/>situation has a
                discouraging<lb/>effect; there have been significant<lb/>return shipments of various
                <lb/>products from New York to <lb/>Europe, among them also [...]<lb/>of tea, and of
                course such <lb/>manipulations necessarily must <lb/>depress the markets over here
                <lb/>heavily. <lb/>We are happy to have </p>
         <pb facs="1864_08_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Gildemeister_Ries_Bremen_4.tif" n="4"/>
         <p>sold the various lots of <lb/>teas + the silk. By the time <lb/>the Trave arrives, we
                will hopefully<lb/>have more favourable conditions, <lb/>we send our greetings in
                <lb/>devoted friendship<lb/>Gildemeister + Ries<lb/>⟨frco⟩</p>
      </body>
   </text>
